{"title":"hsl to hex converter","description":"A program that allows you to quickly convert hsl to hex online.","content":"## About the hsl to hex converter\r\nThis converter allows you to convert a color represented by the **HSL** color model to **HEX**\r\nAs a result of the conversion, you will get a string representing the given color according to the **HEX** model.\r\nThis string has the form `#{red}{green}{blue}`, where each color is written in hexadecimal notation.\r\nThis program can also perform reverse conversion, that is, [convert hex to hsl](/en/color/hex_to_hsl).\r\n\r\n## How to convert hsl to hex\r\nTo convert hsl to hex, enter the value of the hue, saturation level and brightness in the appropriate fields.\r\nThe **HEX** value will be immediately calculated and displayed in the corresponding field of the palette."}